is the file extension literally `jpg.ibdoc` ? we don’t support uploading ibdocs into Build/Converse projects

i’m not sure why the digitization job is trying to call the `barcode_qrcode_detection`, which you probably don’t have in your local environment

do you have any special digitization settings in your Build/Converse project?
